description: Belfast's parade has been postponed along with all parades in the Republic of Ireland.
title: Coronavirus: Irish St Patrick's Day parades cancelled
title_page: Coronavirus: Irish St Patrick's Day parades cancelled - BBC News
maintext: The UK government has said its advice could change in the next 10 to 14 days to have people who show "even minor" signs of respiratory tract infections to self-isolate in an effort to tackle the outbreak.
